snippet.title: BLACK ROSE | Can Two Cops Stop a Killer on the Streets of Hollywood? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A troubling case draws international attention to Los Angeles.
Solving it will require an uneasy partnership and relentless pursuit.

When a series of crimes targets young women in Hollywood, the LAPD turns to an experienced Russian police major for help. Working alongside local detectives, he follows a growing pattern that points to a calculating and dangerous individual. As the investigation deepens, the partnership is tested and the race to stop the person responsible becomes more urgent.

Director: Alexander Nevsky
Cast: Alexander Nevsky, Kristanna Loken, Robert Davi, Adrian Paul.
